snippet.title: Levelhead - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Shipping on April 30th, 2020: pre-registration and pre-purchases available now!

Visit http://levelhead.bscotch.net/ to learn more.

Join the discord @ discord.gg/bscotch

Build, play, share and compete in Levelhead, the platformer maker. Create challenging levels with the deep, intuitive systems of the level editor, then share those levels with the world and gain a following!

Play the Levels from the trailer, made by current players (and occasionally lightly modified for the trailer):
Editor: "Destroy Package, Earn Goal" by TalkGibberish https://levelhead.io/+63nm3r2
Fireballs: "Unfortunate Forest Delivery" by Spekio https://levelhead.io/+x79zdt2
Boombox level: TimConceivable https://levelhead.io/@rmk4os
Teleporting Shark: "Temple Quest" by TheViralMelon https://levelhead.io/+f1wj2z1
Calculator: "Stack Machine 2" by Joe Ah Oh https://levelhead.io/+pxr00nr
Speedrun:  "Under Risk Of Death" by SleepyDoof https://levelhead.io/+3gj8crk
Troll: "Good Troll, Bad Troll" by PureKnickers https://levelhead.io/+b45mszc
Pinball:  "Welcome 2 Ping Bump, Friend!" by Egomouse https://levelhead.io/+14jdd6z

Additional Voice Talent by Aimee Smith - https://www.aimeesmithva.com/
